  englishHref={getTermsHref('en')}
  kicker="Legal"
  portugueseHref={getTermsHref('pt-br')}
  title="Terms and Conditions"
>
  <h2>Use of the site</h2>
  <p>
    You may browse, read, and use SeniorPath for personal and professional learning purposes. You may not misuse
    the service, interfere with its operation, or reproduce paid or proprietary material beyond what applicable
    law allows.
  </p>

  <h2>Content</h2>
  <p>
    The guides, maps, and reference material are provided for educational purposes. They reflect editorial
    judgment and may evolve over time as content is updated or refined.
  </p>

  <h2>Availability</h2>
  <p>
    SeniorPath may change, suspend, or remove parts of the experience at any time, including content structure,
    features, and navigation.
  </p>

  <h2>Liability</h2>
  <p>
    The service is provided on an as-is basis. SeniorPath is not liable for indirect damages, business loss, or
    outcomes resulting from how content is interpreted or applied.
  </p>
</StaticArticlePage>
